#-------------------------------#
# VARIANT PROCESSING PIPELINE   #
#-------------------------------#

This code processes the raw phased 1KPG VCF data (Saini et al 2018) in
order to produce, for every CODIS STR, a file od surrounding SNPs with all
relevant variant characteristics (e.g. MAF, pop-MAF, distance, payseur D)
for downstream analyses.

----------------------------------------------------

input:    /data/processed/
            [CODIS_STR]_withSTR_GT.vcf

outputs:  /data/processed/
            [CODIS_STR]snps.csv 
